      <title>石破茂称日本将向特朗普寻求稳定的能源供应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/ishiba-says-japan-will-seek-stable-energy-supply-from-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相石破茂表示，他将在与美国总统唐纳德·特朗普会晤时要求其提供稳定的能源供应，这暗示日本领导人可能在即将举行的会谈中与特朗普达成协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/ishiba-says-japan-will-seek-stable-energy-supply-from-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 03:26:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普为就职典礼从加密货币公司筹集了数百万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-raised-millions-from-crypto-firms-for-his-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[参议院公共记录办公室提交的文件显示，唐纳德·特朗普总统的就职委员会从加密货币行业的公司那里获得了数百万美元的捐款，而加密货币行业已经受到了特朗普政府的特别关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-raised-millions-from-crypto-firms-for-his-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 01:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赫格塞斯与日本防卫大臣同意加强军事关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/hegseth-japan-defense-minister-agree-to-beef-up-military-ties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本防卫省称，美国国防部长皮特·赫格塞斯和日本防卫大臣在首次通话中同意扩大两国在东海日本岛屿周围的联合军事存在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/hegseth-japan-defense-minister-agree-to-beef-up-military-ties</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 00:54:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普加大与加拿大、墨西哥和中国的关税对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-barrels-toward-tariff-showdown-with-canada-mexico-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普准备于周六征收第一波关税，这将促使外国政府和企业纷纷避开潜在的关税并准备采取报复行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-barrels-toward-tariff-showdown-with-canada-mexico-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 00:03:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普新关税计划的目标是什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-tariffs-what-s-he-trying-to-achieve-for-us-economy-and-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普在竞选期间承诺立即对美国进口产品征收一系列关税，如今他重申计划从 2 月 1 日起对来自加拿大和墨西哥的进口产品征收 25% 的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-tariffs-what-s-he-trying-to-achieve-for-us-economy-and-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 21:58:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税誓言给加拿大、墨西哥和中国带来压力 外汇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-s-25-tariff-vows-send-canada-mexico-currencies-tumbling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普再次承诺于 2 月 1 日对来自加拿大和墨西哥的进口产品征收 25% 的关税，这在纽约交易时段尾盘震动了外汇市场，导致两国货币兑美元大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-s-25-tariff-vows-send-canada-mexico-currencies-tumbling</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 21:08:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将于周六对加拿大、墨西哥征收 25% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-says-he-ll-hit-canada-mexico-with-25-tariffs-on-saturday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将履行威胁，于 2 月 1 日对来自加拿大和墨西哥的进口产品征收 25% 的关税，他做出这一决定的原因包括芬太尼的流动和巨大的贸易逆差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-says-he-ll-hit-canada-mexico-with-25-tariffs-on-saturday</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 20:48:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署行政备忘录，针对联邦航空管理局多元化计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-signs-executive-action-targeting-faa-diversity-practices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普签署了一项行政命令，指示联邦机构取消交通部和联邦航空管理局的多元化、公平和包容性做法，他指责这些做法导致了华盛顿附近机场一架客机与军用直升机空中相撞致人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-signs-executive-action-targeting-faa-diversity-practices</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 20:42:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>根据将养老院出售给私募股权的计划，老年人将面临被驱逐</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/pe-buyout-of-new-york-retirement-home-threatens-to-evict-seniors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坐轮椅的泰瑞·盖尔伯格在长岛北岸的退休社区 Harborside 住了将近二十年。这本应是这位患有记忆问题的 99 岁老人的最后一个家，但这家破产的养老院计划出售给一家私募股权公司，这可能会颠覆她的护理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/pe-buyout-of-new-york-retirement-home-threatens-to-evict-seniors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 19:53:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在空中相撞后抨击 FAA 的 DEI 项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-attacks-faa-diversity-programs-following-mid-air-collision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普迅速将美国航空集团公司一架支线飞机与一架军用直升机的空难政治化，将这起十多年来美国最严重的商业航空事故归咎于多元化、公平和包容计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/trump-attacks-faa-diversity-programs-following-mid-air-collision</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 17:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
